Class Runtime<P extends Protocol>

  org.princehouse.mica.base.model.Runtime<P>
Type Parameters:

Direct Known Subclasses:
SimpleRuntime
public abstract class Runtime<P extends Protocol>
  
extends java.lang.Object

The Runtime instance represents the local node in the gossip network. It runs the local protocol instance with the help of a RuntimeAgent, generated by a Compiler instance. To launch your own protocol, see the SimpleRuntime.launch method.

Author:
lonnie
